casebody.data:
Flor JOHNSON
v.
Capree RICKETTS No. 190P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 14, 2019 Capree Ricketts, for Ricketts, Capree. Patrick S. Lineberry, Attorney at Law, for Johnson, Flor. Timothy W. Gray, Attorney at Law, Greensboro, for P & P of Asheboro, LLC. Flor Johnson, for Johnson, Flor.

ORDER

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of May 2019 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 24th of May 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
